{"tid":612502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣成日都病？","createTime":"2018-04-01T01:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T03:00:14.000Z","uid":34802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1977cccacfb08a7f3ba95df1dfc4b5a5a761bdfd","tid":612502,"uid":34802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T01:27:26.000Z","msg":"我成日都病，身邊啲人一病，通常好易傳染到比我<br />\n我通常一病，就病兩三個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n打咗流感針都仲係咁<br />\n<br />\n細細嗰2歲左右 <br />\n因為發燒入院，仲俾人抽骨髓 <br />\n我阿媽仲同我講 我抽骨髓個刻喊到癲<br />\n不過我仲細，好彩就唔記得咗喇<br />\n<br />\n近排我roommate 病，又唔帶口罩，我嚟㗎又病啦<br />\n本身上禮拜都好返好多，呢家又病過<br />\n<br />\n嚟㗎仲發緊燒，本身諗住呢個假期可以做吓 assignment同溫吓書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62ef2f762a72c42eed727b396b30423f0e391f1","tid":612502,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"抵抗力差囉<br />\n打流感針唔係大晒"},{"pid":"a26b412a5a844026a57780165d528ecf1c7fa975","tid":612502,"uid":34802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f62ef2f762a72c42eed727b396b30423f0e391f1","tid":612502,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"抵抗力差囉<br />\n打流感針唔係大晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T01:33:51.000Z","msg":"我知呀，都係諗住睇吓有冇好啲<br />\n<br />\n我已經每個禮拜做運動啦"},{"pid":"4e0f45dc4b5b320e8d0a478fecf152019238200a","tid":612502,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T01:41:27.000Z","msg":"出街戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebfc82c82c10f76541992b287f8ac6f76a44958","tid":612502,"uid":88853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:42:30.000Z","msg":"小病是福呀<br />\n咁都要咁大負面情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be10dc93f1b45db36374291d8fc8bf67f1221d24","tid":612502,"uid":29773,"like":0,"dislike